channel.title: [PI] dungeoneering max level 120
channel.description: how do i make the max dungeoneering level 120?

item.title: [PI] dungeoneering max level 120
item.dc:creator: @killerjens9 killerjens9
item.description:
@killerjens9 wrote:

Open up, skills.java
Look for “public int getLevelForXp(int skill) {”
Scroll down a bit and look for this: for(int lvl = 1; lvl < 100; lvl++) {
Change that into this: for(int lvl = 1; lvl <= (skill == DUNGEONEERING ? 120 : 99); lvl++) {

Then down a bit more, you should see “return 99”, change that into this: return skill == DUNGEONEERING ? 120 : 99;

And that should do it!
